  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><a href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/ARIA/apg/practices/keyboard-interface/#kbd_roving_tabindex">Roving tabindex</a></td>
    <td>WAI-ARIA APG (Managing Focus)</td>
    <td>Exactly one cell is <code>tabindex="0"</code> and all others <code>-1</code>; the value moves with focus, so <kbd>Tab</kbd> enters/leaves the grid as one stop while the arrows move <em>within</em></td>
  </tr>
